---
import Title from './atoms/Title.astro';
---

<section id="testimonials" class="py-20 w-full">
    <div class="max-w-[var(--max-width)] mx-auto px-4">
        <Title contenido="Client Testimonials" />
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mt-12">
            <div class="testimonial-card">
                <p class="quote">"Working with Nicolas was a game-changer for our company. His ability to integrate AI solutions into our existing systems significantly improved our efficiency. He is a true problem solver who delivers exceptional results."</p>
                <div class="author">
                    <strong>Alex Martinez</strong>
                    <span>COO at InnovateTech</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="testimonial-card">
                <p class="quote">"Nicolas's expertise in both business and technology is unparalleled. He helped us navigate complex blockchain implementation with ease, and his strategic insights were invaluable."</p>
                <div class="author">
                    <strong>Sarah Lee</strong>
                    <span>Head of Operations at SecureChain</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="testimonial-card">
                <p class="quote">"His approach to solving problems is methodical and innovative. Nicolas not only developed a custom software solution for us but also provided guidance that helped us optimize our processes."</p>
                <div class="author">
                    <strong>David Brown</strong>
                    <span>CEO at Global Manufacturing Inc.</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .testimonial-card {
        background: rgba(123, 74, 226, 0.1);
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 2.5rem;
        border: 1px solid rgba(123, 74, 226, 0.2);
        transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .testimonial-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        background: rgba(123, 74, 226, 0.15);
    }

    .quote {
        font-size: 1.6rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: var(--primary-90);
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        font-style: italic;
    }

    .author {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .author strong {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
        color: var(--primary-100);
        background: var(--text-gradient);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    }

    .author span {
        font-size: 1.4rem;
        color: var(--primary-80);
    }
</style> 